Text.Value: Where are you from?
What were you trying to achieve?
Wizard... archmage... companion...
Leave.
Wizard... archmage... wielder of the Weave...
What becomes of a wizard after death?
What is your profession?
When your sky dims... I will be there... waiting...
Avoiding... ceremorphosis... removing... tadpole...
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*
Do you have any last words for me?
How did you die?
Seeking... another way... to fight... to win...
Waterdeep...
Gale... Dekarios...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Without knowing... without feeling... choking on darkness...
How did you get here?
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Seeking... Karsus' power... failed...
Who are you?
Ending... the Absolute... with a bang...
Not concentrating... my magic... not focused...
Bring me back... cast the spell... utmost... importance...
Elminster came... offered solution... turned... Orin... taken...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Why are you so insistent I resurrect you?
Bring me back... before... too late... must cast the spell...
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: Gale has been evicted from the party, then killed.
